{"title":"Sweet Protection Goes Full Summer Send with Hyper Violet Color Drop","link":"https://bikerumor.com/sweet-protection-goes-full-summer-send-with-hyper-violet-color-drop/","date":1747392900000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-gravel--1536x1025.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1025\" alt=\"Sweet Protection Hyper Violet Summer Color Drop gravel\" /></p>\n<p>Sweet Protection just lit the match on summer style with their new Hyper Violet colorway — this one <em>pops</em>! Whether dropping into chunky singletrack or hammering road and gravel miles, the new Hyper Violet Fade and Black Hyper Violet options add a nice summer flash to Sweet Protection’s multi-discipline helmet lineup.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Hyper Violet = Maximum Send Energy</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-road--jpg-e1746810347665.webp\"><img width=\"5580\" height=\"4616\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-road--jpg-e1746810347665.webp\" alt=\"Sweet Protection Hyper Violet Summer Color Drop road\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-road--jpg-e1746810347665.webp 5580w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-road--jpg-e1746810347665-297x246.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-road--jpg-e1746810347665-120x99.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-road--jpg-e1746810347665-768x635.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-road--jpg-e1746810347665-1536x1271.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-road--jpg-e1746810347665-2048x1694.webp 2048w\" /></a><figcaption><em>(Photos/Sweet Protection)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Sweet Protection leans into the <em>look fast, go fast</em> ethos, and Hyper Violet is pure adrenaline in pigment form. They say it’s <em>“inspired by the intensity of the outdoors and the adrenaline of high-speed pursuits</em>” — I agree. It’s bold, confident, and fun—everything we want to be on the bike.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Style Meets Send</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-scaled-e1746810231892.webp\"><img width=\"1707\" height=\"922\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-scaled-e1746810231892.webp\" alt=\"Sweet Protection Hyper Violet Summer Color Drop\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-scaled-e1746810231892.webp 1707w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-scaled-e1746810231892-297x160.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-scaled-e1746810231892-1536x830.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-scaled-e1746810231892-120x65.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-scaled-e1746810231892-768x415.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>What is that color? </em></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sweet Protection calls it Hyper Violet Fade. The color starts from deep electric purple, and fades to a high-voltage blue burst – kind of like a lightning strike caught mid-strike. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-falconeer-.webp\"><img width=\"2362\" height=\"1575\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-falconeer-edited.webp\" alt=\"Sweet Protection Hyper Violet Summer Color Drop falconer\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-falconeer-edited.webp 2362w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-falconeer-edited-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-falconeer-edited-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-falconeer-edited-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-falconeer-edited-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-falconeer-edited-2048x1366.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-falconeer-edited-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-falconeer-edited-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Meanwhile, Black Hyper Violet keeps it a bit more stealthy but still edgy — more “silent killer” than a neon peacock, but still impossible to ignore, offering a style and companion color to your rider expression. That’s especially evident in the Falconer, which can tuck most of that color under its snap-in magnetic Aero vent covers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>And it’s not just a paint job on a couple of helmets. This limited drop hits nine top-tier models across MTB, road, and paddle sports. No matter what you’re bombing down, this collection will hold up and stand out.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Sweet Protection Helmets Getting the Hyper Violet Treatment</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-visor-.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-visor--1536x1536.webp\" alt=\"Sweet Protection Hyper Violet Summer Color Drop visor\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-visor--1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-visor--297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-visor--120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-visor--768x768.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-visor--2048x2048.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-aero-covers-on-.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1537\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-aero-covers-on--1536x1537.webp\" alt=\"Sweet Protection Hyper Violet Summer Color Drop aero covers on\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-aero-covers-on--1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-aero-covers-on--297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-aero-covers-on--120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-aero-covers-on--768x768.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-aero-covers-on--2048x2048.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-full-facer.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1536\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-full-facer-1536x1536.webp\" alt=\"Sweet Protection Hyper Violet Summer Color Drop full facer\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-full-facer-1536x1536.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-full-facer-297x297.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-full-facer-120x120.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-full-facer-768x768.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Sweet-Protection-Hyper-Violet-Summer-Color-Drop-full-facer-2048x2048.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Here’s what’s getting the Hyper Violet makeover:</em></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://backcountry.tnu8.net/c/381569/358742/5311?u=https%253A%252F%252Fwww.backcountry.com%252Fsweet-protection-strayer-2vi-mips-full-face-helmet\"><strong>Strayer 2Vi MIPS</strong> </a>— A full-face gravity helmet that’s just as at home in the bike park as on an enduro stage.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://backcountry.tnu8.net/c/381569/358742/5311?u=https%253A%252F%252Fwww.backcountry.com%252Fsweet-protection-falconer-aero-2vi-mips-helmet\">Falconer (Aero) 2Vi MIPS</a></strong> — The road helmet for the rider who thinks aero gains and style points are equally important. Inspired by nature’s fastest flyer, it’s made to slice the wind and turn heads.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://backcountry.tnu8.net/c/381569/358742/5311?u=https%253A%252F%252Fwww.backcountry.com%252Fsweet-protection-bushwhacker-2vi-mips-helmet\">Bushwhacker 2Vi MIPS</a></strong> — Trail junkies, rejoice. This lid is the go-to for big missions, climbs, and descents. Now in purple.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://backcountry.tnu8.net/c/381569/358742/5311?u=https%253A%252F%252Fwww.backcountry.com%252Fsweet-protection-primer-mips-helmet\">Primer MIPS</a></strong> — XC and trail riders who don’t need anything less than full-featured protection will dig the Primer. It’s all about comfort, coverage, and a dialed fit, now with extra flare.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>And if you’re riding detours to the rapids, good news — the color drop carries over into Sweet’s paddle gear, too.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The new colorway is available now online and through select Sweet retailers.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.sweetprotection.com\" target=\"_blank\"><em>SweetProtection.com</em></a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/sweet-protection-goes-full-summer-send-with-hyper-violet-color-drop/\">Sweet Protection Goes Full Summer Send with Hyper Violet Color Drop</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jordan Villella","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"86c8ce476105089b693d0ceb77ebd593a6ec867284d8db09dd2b0a0ad4f2a4a7","category":"Cycling"}